The build failure is caused by an outdated Makefile target in the spec file. Recent Ollama versions dropped the `build` alias and only ship the `ollama` target. Additionally, note that **Ollama is a Go/C++ project**, not Rust, so the Rust packaging guidelines do not apply here.

Apply this minimal patch to fix the `%build` section:

```diff
@@ -... +... @@
  %build
